### `rxe.mantine.pills_input`

Utility component for displaying tags/labels. No built-in logic - renders children only.

```python
import reflex as rx
import reflex_enterprise as rxe

class PillInputState(rx.State):
    tags: set = {"Foo", "Bar"}

    @rx.event
    def add_tag(self, tag: str):
        self.tags.add(tag)

    @rx.event
    def remove_tag(self, tag: str):
        self.tags.remove(tag)

def pills_input_page():
    return rxe.mantine.pills_input(
        rxe.mantine.pill.group(
            rx.foreach(
                PillInputState.tags,
                lambda tag: rxe.mantine.pill(
                    tag,
                    with_remove_button=True,
                    on_remove=PillInputState.remove_tag(tag),
                ),
            ),
            rxe.mantine.pills_input.field(
                placeholder="Enter tags",
            ),
        ),
        label="PillsInput",
        id="pills-input",
        value=["tag1", "tag2"],
    )
```

